summary:
Just to let you know I at one point suffered multiple migraines a day for over a month
I got nothing done
Nothing helped
The...
body:
Just to let you know I at one point suffered multiple migraines a day for over a month

I got nothing done

Nothing helped

The doctors couldn’t find why

Then my GP asked if I had been to the dentist

Me: no? My teeth don’t hurt?

Him: go get checked and come back here if your teeth are fine

Turned out both my upper wisdom teeth (which had come down naturally over a few years) had massive cavities and needed to be pulled. The doctor pulled them then and there for me and immediately my migraines stopped

And here’s the thing. I never once had a sore tooth or mouth pain. Just migraines.

So if you are having constant headaches or migraines for seemingly no reason it’s sensible to get your teeth checked

summary: Okay, I am not going to lie - this got me a little down. It can be a little difficult when you don’t see the number physically...
body:
1.10.19 - 272.2 (-3.4)


Okay, I am not going to lie - this got me a little down. It can be a little difficult when you don’t see the number physically going down. BUT like I also told all of you, I use Happy Scale - and it is moments like this that are exactly why. I ate well yesterday, but I also ate A LOT. And I was feeling kind of “meh” yesterday for lack of a better word. So honestly seeing a small jump wasn’t unexpected - just annoying. The cool thing is that Happy Scale reminds me that my AVERAGE weight is still going down. It went from 272.7 yesterday, to 272.5 today. And knowing that reminds me that I am still making progress 💪🏻


I told you guys that I would talk about the Itworks cleanse today though, so I’ll do that quickly! So when people thing of cleanses they often time think of something time consuming, difficult, and messy! Something that has you running to the bathroom all the time 🚽 But that isn’t the case with this cleanse! It is two days, four bottles. You take one in the morning before breakfast, and one at night before supper. You eat, but as clean as you can, and drink tooooooons of water! It doesn’t send you running to the bathroom all day, but it still cleans out all the nasty sludge your body is hanging on to. I figured it was a good way to start the year!


This was one of the first Itworks products I tried (that I actually bought, anyway!) and I loved it. As you guys know, I have PCOS. I was having A LOT of trouble losing weight. This product kind of kickstarted my weight loss, because although I didn’t see the crazy like - 8 lbs in 2 days - that some people boast, the Scale went down and continued to after that. 🙌🏻


I didn’t do my wrap last night because I really wanted to shower and wash up, and your not supposed to use soap to clean up right before a wrap because it may clog your pores. Sooooooo I’ll be doing that tonight instead. And I’m going to work ok eating a littleeeeeee cleaner today. Wish me luck, friends!

summary: The Right Way To Do Reverse Lunges
title: The Right Way To Do Reverse Lunges
body:
